This project is the LangGraph-side counterpart to the durable-streams / StreamDB
frontend runtime (rheoDS, https://github.com/dkachur1/rheods, and
@assistant-ui/react-durable-streams,
https://github.com/dkachur1/react-durable-streams). The translator originated as
an internal LangGraph adapter and was extracted and generalized into this
standalone, application-neutral package.
